videos.headline: Bama's Young explodes in record-setting win over Hogs
videos.description: No. 2 Alabama's Bryce Young throws for a school-record 561 yards (second most in SEC history) and five touchdowns to defeat relentless No. 21 Arkansas, 42-35.
